    <img src="/img/blog/hero-excel-vs-sheets.png" alt="Excel vs Google Sheets para empresas y PYMES en 2026" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90" />
    
    <!-- Floating Label -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4 pointer-events-none">
